data.description: A great investment opportunity awaits with this duplex in Horizon. Both units are beautiful with open floor plans, 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, a loft and a private backyard with a covered patio. Other features include refrigerated air, utility rooms, and separate utility meters for each unit. The Master Suites are NICE...with double vanities and soaking garden tubs, separate showers, and huge walk-in closets. This property is an excellent location in Horizon with quick and easy access to retail and restaurants. Make your move, and make this your next great investment.
